rComments: His lectures are on par if you go to class. The assignments cover what was in the lectures. Midterm reflects class notes. Final was tricky, but the professor bell curved. He is always available for office time and helps you out if you see him.

You could tell it was his first time teaching a class. Final was wayy harder than expected, with questions covering topics we'd seen for maybe 10 minutes. He was quick to answer emails and helpful if you needed help outside of class and his lecture notes were good. Assignments were fair
